						<summary>

						<p>This is engraved in peculiar characters and the meaning is obscure. It purports to be a document <hi rend="italic">(sādanam)</hi> with a duplicate in copper-plate (?), issued by the <hi rend="italic">nagarattār</hi> and the <hi rend="italic">padi</hi> assembled together, making a grant of a thousand <hi rend="italic">kalam</hi> of paddy “to this god”.</p>						

						</summary>
